data.description: This 4 bedroom 2 bath home in Delta schools has been generationally owned and loved by the same family that built it. The home offers hardwood floors, updated eat in kitchen and bathroom, new roof, and newer boiler. The front living room offers a fireplace and the back living area could also make for a great owner's suite. The mudroom conversion to a laundry area has been started if you would like to relocate washer and dryer. You will love the attached garage that offers a heated floor and additionally there is a 4 car AND a 2 car detached garage! The back yard has ample room for entertaining and a concrete area that has been a basketball court.
